   - Any modifications or improvements to the Software must be published under the same terms as this Agreement (GPL).

3. Official Backdoor:
   - The Software includes an official backdoor that sends encrypted data to designated security servicesâ€™ servers.
   - All data is encrypted with the user's password and can only be provided to authorities if there is solid evidence of illegal Software use.
   - Data transmission is permitted only after an automatic review by our open-source reviewing software. Security agencies may propose changes to this software, which must be approved by the majority of users through a tamper-proof public poll.

4. Data Transmission Conditions:
