   - If any provision of this Agreement is found to be invalid, it shall not affect the validity of the remaining provisions.

12. Versioning and Access:
   - The official start of product use and the opening of public access for contributions and modifications will commence with versions v1.0.0+.
   - Until then, only individual modifications will be allowed, made by the current head of the company or the development team, without public discussions or changes.
